{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"ida7cb8679-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s500d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"500d"},"text":"§ 500d.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Electromagnetic spectrum superiority implementation plan","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"ida7cb867a-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s500d/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"In General","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The Chief Information Officer of the Department of Defense shall be responsible for oversight of the electromagnetic superiority implementation plan.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"ida7cb867b-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s500d/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Report Required","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Concurrent with the submission of the budget of the President to Congress under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t31/s1105/a"},"text":"section 1105(a) of title 31","children":[],"tail":" for each of fiscal years 2025 through 2029, the Chief Information Officer shall submit to the congressional defense committees a report that includes the following with respect to the electromagnetic superiority implementation plan:"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida7cb867c-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s500d/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The implementation plan in effect as of the date of the report, noting any revisions from the preceding plan.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida7cb867d-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s500d/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" A statement of the elements of the implementation plan that have been achieved.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida7cb867e-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s500d/b/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" For each element that has been achieved, an assessment of whether the element is having its intended effect.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida7cb867f-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s500d/b/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" For any element that has not been achieved, an assessment of progress made in achieving the element, including a description of any obstacles that may hinder further progress.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida7cb8680-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s500d/b/5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5"},"text":"(5)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" For any element that has been removed from the implementation plan, a description of the reason for the removal of the element and an assessment of the impact of not pursuing achievement of the element.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida7cb8681-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s500d/b/6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"6"},"text":"(6)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Such additional matters as the Chief Information Officer considers appropriate.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"ida7cb8682-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s500d/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Electromagnetic Superiority Implementation Plan Defined","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"In this section, the term “electromagnetic superiority implementation plan” means the Electromagnetic Superiority Implementation Plan signed by the Secretary of Defense on ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2021-07-15"},"text":"July 15, 2021","children":[],"tail":", and any successor plan."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"ida7cb8683-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/118/31/dA/tXVI/s1682/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 118–31, div. A, title XVI, § 1682(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2023-12-22"},"text":"Dec. 22, 2023","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/137/615"},"text":"137 Stat. 615","children":[],"tail":", § 504; renumbered § 500d, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/118/159/dA/tXVII/s1701/a/10"},"text":"Pub. L. 118–159, div. A, title XVII, § 1701(a)(10)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2024-12-23"},"text":"Dec. 23, 2024","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/138/2203"},"text":"138 Stat. 2203","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"ida7cb8684-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"ida7cb8685-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"ida7cb8686-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2024—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/118/159"},"text":"Pub. L. 118–159","children":[],"tail":" renumbered "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s504"},"text":"section 504 of this title","children":[],"tail":", relating to an electromagnetic spectrum superiority implementation plan, as this section."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
